I pledge to be intentional and mentor women for leadership roles. #BeEqual
I pledge to be flexible and accommodate for work-life balance. #BeEqual
I pledge to be vocal and give people an opportunity to speak up. #BeEqual
I pledge to be aware and hire the best qualified people even if they are different than me. #BeEqual
I pledge to be proactive and implement change within my own team. #BeEqual
